main event: Two witnesses observed six very bright red spherical lights traveling in a single file formation between Crestview and Milton, Florida on September 28, 1967.
interesting points: The lights moved in a single file and circled around the witnesses,The objects emitted a low pitch humming sound when the car windows were rolled down,An additional red light was spotted in the woods nearby that was not part of the original six,There was no physical evidence or photographs included in the report,After circling the area, the objects buzzed the witnesses before the sighting ended.
sighted object: six very bright red spherical lights
